SubjectRegulations Amending and Repealing Certain Regulations Administered by the Minister of Veterans Affairs (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending and Repealing Certain Regulations Administered by the Minister of Veterans Affairs (Miscellaneous Program) in order to correct typographical errors and a discrepancy between the French and the English versions. The Vetcraft Shops Regulations and a subsection of the Veterans Allowance Regulations are repealed.
